cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a new way for LSTM training, which is a widely used recurrent structure in sequence modeling. The focus is on controlling information flow through gates, which is a key aspect of LSTM. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and computer vision (cs.CV).
